column5: 1 cancellation and another cant join for personal reasons. Targeting trout. pike Meet up in the hammer or grimsby I have a hut, heater, etc pm me if you wish to join. back by 1pm.
Go get 'em, Vince.  If I didn't have to work, I'd be up for it.

Evenin!  PMs won't work..  Hope I'm not too late.  If you've still got a spot, I'm down.  Been out 3 times and I'm getting tired of eating skunk.  Got gear plus plenty of emeralds.  Can intercept you wherever.  cheers!
wish i saw this last night, i forsure would have been down for meeting up again hopefully with better results too
